{"tid":2508674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東10歲男童當街燒4車　原因竟為「想看車爆炸飛起來」","createTime":"2021-04-29T02:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T04:56:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"12ba0dde9b0dc94be2f8c03724f28191c8244a02","tid":2508674,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"廣東陽江市近日4輛泊在路邊的車先後突然起火，警方追查後，發現事件的始作俑者竟是一名年僅10歲的男童，他到案後坦言是因在電視上看到爆炸覺得非常刺激才放火燒車，「想看車爆炸飛起來」。<br />\n<br />\n本月18日，警方獲報指石灣村舊寨有2輛汽車起火，起火部位均為小汽車車頭處。消防員接報後立即趕赴現場把火撲滅，同時警方發現距離兩車100米處，還有一輛紅色小汽車尾部有輕微燒過的痕跡。其實，這已非當地近日首次有汽車被縱火，早在11日，一輛白色雪佛蘭（Chevrolet）車也被點燃。<br />\n<br />\n經查，原來4輛車被燒都是一名居住在附近的10歲男童所為，他事後自述點火原因，稱他是因為覺得電視上的爆炸很刺激，好奇之下就點火燒車，想看車爆炸飛起來的畫面。根據內地法律規定，不滿16周歲者放火罪不予刑事處罰，責令家長加以管教，而火災造成的損失由家長或監護人承擔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210428/464106294597390336749351.jpeg/A3f757Pc72HYTOfys_MZ-kcwd-2IwtGWyKBEY8igRGM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210428%2F464106294597390336749351.jpeg%2FA3f757Pc72HYTOfys_MZ-kcwd-2IwtGWyKBEY8igRGM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=d1736fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210428/464108335243726848048519.jpeg/-avIQj8wKsPa2xkdmLs6wNdDwXy5Q8aSm_zV1Jv81dQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210428%2F464108335243726848048519.jpeg%2F-avIQj8wKsPa2xkdmLs6wNdDwXy5Q8aSm_zV1Jv81dQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=cffef002&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210428/464108336921579520926735.jpeg/8wB2oVMXbqHMnW-XzCHXW_74neAXpnW6OR_veDkf73g?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210428%2F464108336921579520926735.jpeg%2F8wB2oVMXbqHMnW-XzCHXW_74neAXpnW6OR_veDkf73g%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fcf69640&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210428/464108338737844224104269.jpeg/N0A99m8y8e5I9wPMXRBVspTHZMycRVHaurdEo7q3RKM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210428%2F464108338737844224104269.jpeg%2FN0A99m8y8e5I9wPMXRBVspTHZMycRVHaurdEo7q3RKM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b114db59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ebbb32db36c5f1036370c6f95eee7776fd8fdb1","tid":2508674,"uid":164374,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"玩GTA咪得LOR...<br />\n定係大陸block咗唔比玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89c73a57f771acf61875c6ae198e887ed1c7cb4","tid":2508674,"uid":83582,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:47:24.000Z","msg":"呢o的時候緊係燒Telsa, 可以唔使賠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2be43c7d88086d0952ba829b7aaf61b698176ea","tid":2508674,"uid":92448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T03:02:11.000Z","msg":"睇埋支那gif 圖po佢咪開心死？"},{"pid":"5ec4f3829eb00e6db5a3c857e636ffa639544f42","tid":2508674,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T03:04:57.000Z","msg":"佢10歲點諗到用咩燃料放火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41eb8c325a0a88b6d1a6b4c8e166e4a052bbb5a4","tid":2508674,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"調酒師太子站外參與縱火 身世坎坷有悔意兼願賠償 被判囚39月<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/606536/%E8%AA%BF%E9%85%92%E5%B8%AB%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB-%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%96%E5%9D%8E%E5%9D%B7%E6%9C%89%E6%82%94%E6%84%8F%E5%85%BC%E9%A1%98%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F-%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A39%E6%9C%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F606536%2F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25A4%